trans-unit.source: Represents data that is sent with a **ManipulationProcessor2D.Completed** event or an **InertiaProcessor2D.Completed** event.

This data applies to either a <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Completed?displayProperty=fullName> event or an <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.InertiaProcessor2D.Completed?displayProperty=fullName> event.
Gets the new x-coordinate of the composite position of the manipulation.

The origin point represented by the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DCompletedEventArgs.OriginX%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DCompletedEventArgs.OriginY%2A> properties is the average position of all manipulators associated with an element.
The new x-coordinate of the composite position of the manipulation.
Gets the new y-coordinate of the composite position of the manipulation.

The origin point represented by the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DCompletedEventArgs.OriginX%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DCompletedEventArgs.OriginY%2A> properties is the average position of all manipulators associated with an element.
The new y-coordinate of the composite position of the manipulation.
Gets the total amount of change since the manipulation started.
The total amount of change since the manipulation started.
Gets the current velocities of the manipulation.
The current velocities of the manipulation.
